(1846, 1, '2014-11-03 19:44:43', '2014-11-03 19:44:43', '[vc_row type="full_width_background" parallax_speed="1" css=".vc_custom_1416777628939{background: #44423f url(http://www.web4.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/12.jpg?id=1872) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" enable_parallax="false" parallax_direction="down" full_height="true"][vc_column width="1/1"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="text-center" type="in_container" parallax_speed="1" css=".vc_custom_1415045123958{padding-top: 65px !important;padding-bottom: 65px !important;}" row_id="info"][vc_column width="1/1" offset="vc_col-lg-offset-3 vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-xs-12"][vc_column_text]<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1881" src="http://www.web4.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/info.png" alt="info" width="71" height="92" />\n\n<span style="color: #111; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300;">W E L C O M E  T H E  F A M I L Y</span>\n\nI only need to pass these guards and I can do it," he said at last. "I know a secret entrance to the palace through the pinnacle of the highest tower. I fell upon it by chance one day as I was passing above the palace on patrol duty.\n\nIn this work it is required that we investigate any unusual occurrence we may witness, and a face peering from the pinnacle of the high tower of the palace was, to me, most unusual.\n\nI therefore drew near and discovered that the possessor of the peering face was none other than Sab Than. He was slightly put out at being detected and commanded me to keep the matter to myself.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1415045085308{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-right: 100px !important;padding-left: 100px !important;}"]<span style="color: #111; font-size: 40px; line-height: 40px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">Style is a way to say who you are without having to speak.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_cus